quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,62,"∆Āeen goong…óin…ďe e …ďeen yahodin…ďe e nasaara en, e …ďe ngalaa diine en ,kala goong…óin…óo Alla e √Īalaande wattan o golli ko mo∆ī∆īi …ďeen ke…ďata njo…ďdi to Joom ma…ď…ďe kulol alanaa …ďe te kam…ďe …ďe cunotaako."
  2,63,"Nde min …ďami aadi mon min ummini fello Tuur dow mon , ∆īettee ko min ngddani on he semmbe ciftoree ko woni heen mbela joo kulon Alla."
  2,64,"Fawii heen caggal …óuum nduŇčti-…óon so wonaano …ďural Alla e yurmeende Makko dow mon maa on njeye e bonnoraa…ďe."
  2,65,"On nganndii …ďeen too√Ī…ďe he mon √Īande hoore-biir (samdi) min mbi'i …ďe ngontee baa…ói booraa…ói."
  2,66,"Min mba…ói …óum woni maande teskuye wonande …ďe e aroyoo…ďe e tinndinoore wonande hul…ďe Alla …ďe."
  2,67,"Muusaa wi'i yim…ďe makko Alla yamirii on nde kirsoton nagge …ďe mbii mbela nanngir-…óaa min ko …óaay…ďe? o wi'i: mi…óo moolii Alla jeyeede e majju…ďe."
  2,68,"∆Āe mbi'i du'ano min Joom maa o la…ď…ďinana min no nge wa'i. O wi'i: ko nagge nge wonaa nayeewe wonaa √Īale ko hakindiinge mba…óee ko njamira-…óon koo."
  2,69,"∆Āe mbi'i torano min Joom maa o la…ď…ďinana min ngoobu (kulor) magge ? O wii: Oon wi'i ko sooye no feewi enge weli laarde."